data.description: PRICE REDUCED-MOTIVATED SELLERS! BETTER THAN NEW 4-bedroom,3-bath CREATIVE HOMES CUSTOM, all on one level. Already fully landscaped with pool & spa! The cozy stone fireplace with gas logs beckons, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere in the living room. Open kitchen & dining area make entertaining a breeze,with plenty of space to gather. Master suite is a true sanctuary, offering a corner garden tub for relaxing baths, separate vanities for added convenience, and ample closet space. A delightful surprise awaits your guests,as one of the BRs features a private bath, & it doubles as a pool bath,making it an excellent addition to your backyard oasis. Step into your backyard paradise, featuring a ONE YEAR OLD HEATED POOL & SPA, surrounded by lush landscaping in front & back yards. Additionally,this home includes a spacious home office, providing the ideal work-from-home space. OVERSIZED PATIO AREA area is perfect for outdoor gatherings & leisurely afternoons in the sun. AC REPLACED 2021!
